  _missions:
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: meetHollin
    Title: A Stranger at the Inn
    Summary: Arrive at the Crooked Pintle and ask for Wren by name.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: hollinReveals
    Title: Hollin's Inheritance
    Summary: Share the page and name her grandmother left her.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: findWitchCottage
    Title: The Witch's Cottage
    Summary: Follow the old path with Wren and Almy.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: wendlightFound
    Title: The Wend's True Course
    Summary: Help trace the river's remembered line.
  - Act: 4
    QuestId: wendSource
    Title: The Source of the Wend
    Summary: Walk upstream with Wren to the clear-cut.
  _quotes:
  - Text: I am walking. And looking for a place my grandmother used to name when
      she thought no one was listening.
    Context: Explaining why she came to Hollowfen.
  - Text: I think the path remembers feet better than names.
    Context: Approaching the old cottage path.
  - Text: Not broken. Loosed.
    Context: Correcting Wren at the source of the Wend.
